summary: DoorDash, Inc. (NASDAQ:DASH) is one of the best stocks to buy according to Jim Simons’ Renaissance Technologies. DoorDash, Inc. headline: DoorDash and Waymo Launch Autonomous Delivery Service and Introduce Limited-Time Waymo Promotion for DashPass Members
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, October 16, 2025--Today, DoorDash, Inc. (Nasdaq: DASH) announced a new partnership with Waymo to launch an autonomous delivery service in Metro Phoenix and introduce a limited-time $10 Waymo promotion for DashPass members in Los Angeles, San Francisco, and Phoenix.
